   281‚Üí   * You can use `safeTry` without this method.
   282‚Üí   * @example
   283‚Üí   * ```typescript
   284‚Üí   * safeTry(function* () {
   285‚Üí   *   const okValue = yield* yourResult
   286‚Üí   * })
   287‚Üí   * ```
   288‚Üí   * Emulates Rust's `?` operator in `safeTry`'s body. See also `safeTry`.
   289‚Üí   */
   290‚Üí  safeUnwrap(): Generator<Err<never, E>, T>
   292‚Üí  /**
